dc_description_s: These polygon and line data layers represent hydrography for Eau Claire County, Wisconsin in 2017. They are feature classes within the geodatabase, EauClaire_Hydro_2017.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are 'Hydro_Anno', 'Hydro_arc', and 'Hydro_poly'.
